data.title: Nasdaq Seeks to Boost Trading Cap for Options on Top Bitcoin ETF
data.description: Nasdaq’s International Securities Exchange proposed quadrupling the daily trading limit for options tied to BlackRock Inc.’s iShares Bitcoin Trust ETF as demand from investors increases.
